Obsoletes:	BashBurn
BuildArch:	noarch
BuildRoot:	%{tmpdir}/%{name}-%{version}-root-%(id -u -n)

%description
BashBurn is a bash script designed to make CD burning at the console
easier. It supports burning normal data CDs, audio CDs, blanking
CD-RWs, multisession, and more.

